<body style="font-family:'Arial';font-size:12pt;text-align:left;"><div style="position:relative;width:103.9pt;height:109.8pt;float:left;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:3.6pt 7.2pt 3.6pt 7.2pt;overflow:hidden;">
<p class="Normal" style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="139" height="138" style="border: 0pt none;margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;" title="embedded image (png)" alt="[image]" /></p>
</div>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;">Ministerul Educaţiei, Cercetării, Tineretului şi Sportului</span></p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;">OLIMPIADA NAŢIONALĂ DE CHIMIE</span></p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;">EDIŢIA a 44-a</span></p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;">PITEŞTI -31 ianuarie-6 februarie 2010</span></p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;">Clasa a VIII-a </span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;">SUBIECTUL I ................................................................................... (20 puncte)</span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;text-indent:18pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">La următorii 10 itemi un singur răspuns este corect. Scrieţi răspunsul corect pe foaia de concurs. Nu se admit ştersături, modificări. </span></p>
<ol style="margin:0pt;padding:0pt;">
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Numărul atomic al elementului al cărui ion E</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sup>2+</sup></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> are următoarea repartiţie de electroni pe straturi: K → xe</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sup>-</sup></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">, L → ye</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sup>-</sup></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">, M → (20-x)e</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sup>-</sup></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">, N → (x + 2y)e</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sup>-</sup></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">, O → ye</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sup>-</sup></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">, este: </span></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:36pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">a. 52		b. 54		c. 56		d. 60		e. 50</span></p>
<ol start="2" style="margin:0pt;padding:0pt;">
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Compuşii: H</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">SO</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>4</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> concentrat, FeS</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">, MgSO</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>4</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">•7H</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">O, CaSO</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>4</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">•2H</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">O, FeO(OH), HNO</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>3</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> se mai cunosc şi sub denumirile:</span></p>
<ol style="margin:0pt;padding:0pt;list-style-type:lower-alpha;">
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Vitriol, sare amară, pirită, gips, rugină, apă tare;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Vitriol, rugină, gips, sare amară, pirită, apă tare;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Vitriol, pirită, sare amară, gips, rugină, apă tare;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Apă tare, pirită, sare amară, gips, rugină, vitriol;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Apă tare, pirită, gips, sare amară, rugină, vitriol.</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">În reacţiile:</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:70pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Cl</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> + H</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> →</span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:70pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Cl</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> + Fe →</span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:70pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Cl</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> + Cu →</span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:70pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Cl</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> + KI →</span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:70pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">rezultă următorii compuşi:</span></p>
<ol style="margin:0pt;padding:0pt;list-style-type:lower-alpha;">
<li style="list-style-type:none;">
<ol style="margin:0pt;padding:0pt;list-style-type:lower-alpha;">
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">HCl; FeCl</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>3</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">; CuCl; I</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> + KCl;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">HCl; FeCl</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>3</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">; CuCl</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">; I</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> + KCl;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">HCl; FeCl</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">; CuCl</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">; I</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> + KCl;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">HCl; nu reacţionează; CuCl</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">; I</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> + KCl;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">HCl; FeCl</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>3</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">; CuCl; nu reacţionează.</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Un oxiacid al sulfului conţine 2,04%H şi 32,653%S. Formula moleculară a acidului este:</span></p>
<ol style="margin:0pt;padding:0pt;list-style-type:lower-alpha;">
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">H</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">SO</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>3</sub></span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">H</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">SO</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>4</sub></span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">H</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">S</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">O</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>3</sub></span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">H</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">S</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>4</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">O</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>6</sub></span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">H</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">SO</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Plantele verzi, la lumină, prin procesul de fotosinteză:</span></p>
<ol style="margin:0pt;padding:0pt;list-style-type:lower-alpha;">
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Consumă O</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> şi elimină CO</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Consumă aer şi elimină CO</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Consumă CO</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> şi elimină O</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Consumă CO</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> şi elimină aer</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Consumă CO şi elimină O</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Un oxid al sulfului, A, este caracterizat prin raportul masic de combinare de 1:1. Este corectă afirmaţia:</span></p>
<ol style="margin:0pt;padding:0pt;list-style-type:lower-alpha;">
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Substanţa A este un oxid de sulf (VI);</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Ecuaţia </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;">2FeS</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"> + 11/2O</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"> → Fe</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;">O</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"><sub>3</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"> + 4A</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">, reprezintă o reacţie chimică de obţinere a oxidului A;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Ecuaţia </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;">Na</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;">SO</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"><sub>3</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"> + 2HCl → 2NaCl + H</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;">O + A</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> reprezintă o reacţie chimică care nu are loc;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Ecuaţia </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;">2FeS</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"> + 11/2O</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"> → Fe</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;">O</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"><sub>3</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-style:italic;"> + 4A</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> reprezintă reacţia de prăjire oxidantă a blendei;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">oxidul de sulf A în reacţie cu apa formează H</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">SO</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>4</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">.</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Este corectă afirmaţia:</span></p>
<ol style="margin:0pt;padding:0pt;list-style-type:lower-alpha;">
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Diamantul are duritate 1 în scara Mohs;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Diamantul este un briliant şlefuit;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Grafitul este opac, de culoare neagră-cenuşie, unsuros la pipăit şi lucios;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Grafitul are densitatea mai mică decât apa;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Grafitul nu conduce curentul electric.</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Este corectă afirmaţia:</span></p>
<ol style="margin:0pt;padding:0pt;list-style-type:lower-alpha;">
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Aluminiul este solid, argintiu, cu luciu metalic şi nu conduce curentul electric;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Limonitul are formula moleculară Fe</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">O</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>3</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">•2H</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">O;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Magnetita conţine 72,41% Fe;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Prin acţiunea apei asupra ferului la 700 ºC se obţine numai Fe</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">O</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>3</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> + H</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Bronzul este un aliaj al cuprului cu zincul.</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">După încălzirea în flacără a unei probe dintr-o placă de cupru pur, masa finală a acesteia este mai mare cu o optime faţă de masa ei iniţială.</span></p>
<ol style="margin:0pt;padding:0pt;list-style-type:lower-alpha;">
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Placa de cupru pur se acoperă cu un strat de culoare albastră;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Ambele substanţe prezente în proba finală reacţionează cu acidul clorhidric;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Compusul rezultat în urma încălzirii în flacără, în reacţie cu hidrogenul conduce la obţinerea compusului C care conţine 96,96% Cu;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Cuprul metalic colorează flacăra incoloră a unui bec de gaz în violet;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Raportul molar dintre substanţele prezente în proba finală este 1:1.</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Afirmaţia corectă este:</span></p>
<ol style="margin:0pt;padding:0pt;list-style-type:lower-alpha;">
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Dacă în 80 grame soluţie de NaOH cu concentraţia procentuală masică 4% se introduc 2,3 grame Na, concentraţia soluţiei creşte la 10%;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Prin barbotarea de anhidridă sulfuroasă în apă, soluţia de turnesol se colorează în albastru;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Prin introducerea unei plăcuţe de staniu într-o soluţie de CuSO</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>4</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">, masa finală a plăcuţei va fi mai mică decât masa ei iniţială;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Sunt compuşi ionici: NH</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>4</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Cl; KH; CCl</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>4</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">, NaOH, CaO;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Dizolvarea NH</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>4</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">NO</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>3</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> solid în apă reprezintă un proces exoterm.</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:54pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;">SUBIECTUL II ................................................................................... (20 puncte)</span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;text-indent:18pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;text-indent:18pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Se dă schema:</span></p>
<ol style="margin:0pt;padding:0pt;">
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="151" height="24" style="border: 0pt none;margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;" title="embedded image (png)" alt="[image]" /></sub></span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="129" height="24" style="border: 0pt none;margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;" title="embedded image (png)" alt="[image]" /></sub></span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="115" height="24" style="border: 0pt none;margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;" title="embedded image (png)" alt="[image]" /></sub></span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="73" height="20" style="border: 0pt none;margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;" title="embedded image (png)" alt="[image]" /></sub></span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="140" height="28" style="border: 0pt none;margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;" title="embedded image (png)" alt="[image]" /></sub></span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="171" height="28" style="border: 0pt none;margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;" title="embedded image (png)" alt="[image]" /></sub></span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="152" height="28" style="border: 0pt none;margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;" title="embedded image (png)" alt="[image]" /></sub></span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="107" height="24" style="border: 0pt none;margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;" title="embedded image (png)" alt="[image]" /></sub></span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="96" height="20" style="border: 0pt none;margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;" title="embedded image (png)" alt="[image]" /></sub></span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="132" height="27" style="border: 0pt none;margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;" title="embedded image (png)" alt="[image]" /></sub></span></p>
<ul style="margin:0pt;padding:0pt;list-style-type:disc;">
<li style="font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Se ştie că substanţa „a” conţine 31,836% K şi 28,979% Cl;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Ecuaţia 2 reprezintă reacţia de obţinere a gazului „e” în laborator. Gazul diatomic „e” conţine elementul care are 7 electroni în stratul al treilea al învelişului electronic; </span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Ecuaţiile 8, 9, 10 reprezintă reacţiile chimice prin care se obţine industrial substanţa „q” ce conţine 43,339% Na şi 11,320% C;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">„m” este un acid al elementului E, al cărui ion trivalent E</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sup>3-</sup></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> este izoelectronic cu gazul rar din perioada a doua;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Substanţa „h” conţine un element al cărui cation colorează flacăra incoloră a unui bec de gaz în roşu cărămiziu, se foloseşte în construcţii și la identificarea gazului „p”;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">„l” se mai numeşte şi ţipirig.</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Scrieţi și egalați ecuaţiile reacţiilor chimice reprezentate în schemă.</span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;">SUBIECTUL III ................................................................................... (20 puncte)</span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> </span></p>
<ol style="margin:0pt;padding:0pt;">
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Se tratează 501 grame soluţie de AlCl</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>3 </sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">de concentraţie procentuală masică 53,293% cu 900 grame soluţie de NaOH de concentraţie procentuală masică 40%. Determinaţi compoziţia procentuală a soluţiei finale, exprimată în procente de moli.</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:18pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> </span></p>
<ol start="2" style="margin:0pt;padding:0pt;">
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:36pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Într-un proces industrial de prăjire a blendei cu aer (20% O</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> în procente de volum) rezultă un amestec gazos ce conţine 15% O</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> (în procente de volum).</span></p>
<ol start="6" style="margin:0pt;padding:0pt;list-style-type:lower-alpha;">
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Calculaţi volumul de aer utilizat în procesul prăjirii oxidante a 2,5 tone blendă de puritate 77,6% (impurităţile nu participă la reacţie);</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Calculaţi numărul de kmoli de amoniac obţinuţi cu azotul separat în urma prăjirii blendei;</span></p>
</li>
<li style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;margin-left:72pt;">
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Calculaţi procentul în moli de O</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>2</sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> transformat. </span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;">SUBIECTUL IV ................................................................................... (30 puncte)</span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">	Tremolitul este o varietate de azbest. În stare naturală tremolitul este un mineral fibros care are în compoziţie Mg, un alt metal divalent necunoscut, oxigen, hidrogen şi un alt nemetal tetravalent. Prin reacţia a 126 grame apă cu un mol din oxidul metalului necunoscut se formează o soluţie în care procentul masic de hidrogen este de 7,692%. Raportul dintre numărul de atomi de Mg şi numărul de atomi de metal necunoscut are valoarea 0,4, iar raportul dintre numărul de atomi de O şi de nemetal necunoscut este de 3:1. În compoziţia unui mol de tremolit intră 144,528•10</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sup>23</sup></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> atomi de O şi 2 atomi-gram de Mg. Ştiind că procentul masic de nemetal necunoscut din tremolit este 26,107%, stabiliţi formula acestuia ţinând cont de rapoartele molare ale oxizilor componenţi.</span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Mase atomice: Al-27; Ca-40; Ba-137; C-12; Cl-35,5; Cu-64; Fe-56; H-1; O-16; K-39, Mg-24; Na-23; Ni-59; Sr-88; Si-28; S-32, Sn-119, Zn-65;</span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">N</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sub>A </sub></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">= 6,022•10</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><sup>23</sup></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> particule/mol</span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;">Se acordă 10 puncte din oficiu</span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;">Timp de lucru 3 ore</span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Subiectele au fost propuse de: prof. dr. Ion Ion, prof. Mihalyfalvi Eva, prof. Șerban Ruxanda, prof. Neacșu Mădălina, prof. Niculae Anca</span></p>
